The paper deals with visual question answering (VQA), which involves understanding natural language questions about images. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also proposes a methodology to train models to learn logical connectives, which involves machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
